{"tid":922308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「致命中國」鷹派白宮顧問納瓦羅將出席G20川習會","createTime":"2018-11-30T09:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T11:02:55.000Z","uid":28765,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d414de9852b77488de9eb0ef31dbe625d10caef","tid":922308,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"2018年11月30日 15:12<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3363/d3363016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3363%2Fd3363016.jpg&h=6f393146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅（達志影像／美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n中美領導人將於12月1日在G20峰會後舉行晚宴，商討化解貿易衝突的對策。港媒引述一名白宮官員說法指稱，白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅（Peter Navarro）也將出席此次的「川習會」。納瓦羅是美國著名的鷹派經濟學家，以其對中美貿易關係變化的激進立場而聞名，出版過《致命中國》等數十部書籍。<br />\n有分析指稱，納瓦羅的出席可以解讀為在向中方發出信號，表明美國政府內部對於貿易衝突「鷹派立場是上升的」。值得一提的是，納瓦羅參與川習會的風聲也讓當天的道瓊工業平均指數短暫跌至低位。<br />\n納瓦羅曾於今年11月公開表示，美國與中國達成的一項潛在協議將取決於川普總統的條款，而不是華爾街的條款，「由於華爾街的參與，任何交易都會出現惡臭。」上述評論同樣導致當天的股市跌至低位。白宮經濟顧問庫德洛（Larry Kudlow）則是否認納瓦羅的言論，認為此人不是在為總統發言，也不是在為政府發言。<br />\n有關貿易戰方面，《華爾街日報》則是引述中美官員的話指稱，兩國正在商討「暫時休戰」，包括美方在2019年春季前不會再調高大陸商品的關稅，以換取更多時間磋商。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 鷹派白宮顧問納瓦羅將出席G20川習會 | ETtoday大陸新聞 | ETtoday新聞雲 手機版 | ETtoday MobileWeb <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181130/1319397.htm#ixzz5YKP1Kaph\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181130%2F1319397.htm%23ixzz5YKP1Kaph&d=x6QnK7izEOu77SqpzK8VevM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=11dad416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181130/1319397.htm#ixzz5YKP1Kaph</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8453645208b86da3b7b4b25ba6077c69ae47a0","tid":922308,"uid":150347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"結果都呼之欲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b42b3a0273e42ffc198312587101b7c966e562c","tid":922308,"uid":77196,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"習帝最唔想見到果條友偏偏就要出現，仲唔激到佢死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5b0509be915b25a244b6b69333c1876e38c2d8","tid":922308,"uid":65352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kXFHqU_V1-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkXFHqU_V1-Q&d=x6QnK7izEOu77SqpzK8VevM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=55e943d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kXFHqU_V1-Q</a>"},{"pid":"d2f26a790ef27828a1598e35a2e1e3bb17e6dfba","tid":922308,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"之前唔係話打入冷宮咩？又返黎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922afb875a1e6b45374f1a3f1add03b687afa79a","tid":922308,"uid":222392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"嘩&hellip;&hellip;Death by China 同 Crouching Tiger"},{"pid":"dcd8afb227a69020665a074eb06d927cf61df4e9","tid":922308,"uid":21602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T10:04:39.000Z","msg":"Navarro&rsquo;s role in the talks has been closely watched in China, with newspapers such as the South China Morning Post viewing his presence as an indicator of whether Trump and Xi can reach a deal. He has taken a harder line on China than others in the Trump administration, criticizing Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin in May for declaring a pause to the trade war and this month warning Wall Street bankers to stop pushing Trump for a quick deal with Xi."},{"pid":"97cb8dfd7aa9378741711c3bd23c706b6eeebdf5","tid":922308,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"